      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOONGALLA AL (6) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at this track over 400m. Makes plenty of appeal. IF HE COULD (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (26.48) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning 10 races. The form from his last run stacks up well. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. XISAN BALE (4) turned in a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Zero Killer (23.12) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings seven times from 12 starts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. SPECIAL PLAYERS (3) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
